title: Dog shows off tractor driving skills
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device Dog shows off tractor driving skills 22 February 2017 Last updated at 18:41 GMT Rambo the dog made a few people paws for thought as he showed off his tractor driving skills in County Down. 
The labrador was filmed at the wheel by owner Albert Reid during a ploughing event in Mount Panther earlier this month. 
But the rumour that Rambo has applied for his driving licence is just a shaggy dog story!
